column2: Yiith e raan ci caal e pinynhoem
Nae caa atheek toe e baai thoek e thai yic gaem ku yithken thong toe e nyiinken, kek aalau enhom ku thong, ku doer e pinynhom.

Ku nae ci yiith e raan mar ekoc nhiim, ku dhalkek bi kuoec loeoei bei epion e raanic, ku  aye raan thoek eben waai bi ben epinynhom bi raan liek e lau enhom e jamdeic, ku theek yanhde, ku ci ben rioc, ku ngong.
Ku na peth bi loeoeng raan aakoeuny, bi raan cii nyany e rin ekoeuc loeui ye loeui yen, ku teng enyin piny.
Ku nae ci wut ethai matyiic, yen gam e coek eloeoengiic loen de raan yith teem kua theek, ku na thoeng moec nhoem kek e tik e yithiic kua ci teem bik roet aakoeuny bi pir piath baai ku leu yic.
Ku na ci bei toe akutic gam bik ka cin mat kek akut e mawuut epinynhom(UN), bik yith e raan ku lau enhoem kua theek aatiit.
Ku na ngic eben loen e yith kak ku lau enhoem aleng koeuny dit kua thek e gem gem ken yic.
Ka kut dit adhel.

coeoet eceel ken yic erin yith e raan, erin yen e ten eroem ethai eben thin, ku(UN), wic bi raan tic e ciengic ku teu ka nyiin piny eceel ken yic, bi athek eyith ku lau enhoem kak coek coekpiny edhoel epioc ku weet ku cer cer ebaiyic ku pinynhoem bi bik tiit. epiny nhoem eben ekem ebei toe akutic, ku thai awen rer toe eke cin.
Wien 1
Raan thoek eben aye dheeth ka lau nhoem kua thoeng nhiim eyithiic, kua thekic, kua ci yeknhiethku puou, ku bik ceng ka ke ye mith etik.
Wien 2

Raan eben aleng yic bi liek eyithiic ku lau enhoemic eceel kenic ka ci tektek ethoek etiel ekuat, ku kit, kemen thai ku thoek ku yanh etheek ku wel ebai kmen wet det loei e rot kemen bai ku cieng bai kemen jeek ku dheth kemen kuat etau det loei e rot ka cin tektek ethoek ekem moe ku tik.
Ku cit te wen ci yen luel, acin tiel toe e wel ebai yic ku loeoeng ku kem ebei ku ten wen rer eraan thin pan ceng kemen ci ceen kemen aci roet mac eroet, kemen toe eraan det cin.
Wien 3
Raan thoek eben aleng yic bi pir ku leu nhoem ku le lang.
Wien 4
Kuat  eraan acii leu bi kool kemen bi loony kuat epec ku loony  thok eben aci peen.
Wien 5
Raan thok eben aciben e leeng kemen bi koeuc yoeng ci min elai, keme bi joor bi ci thek.
Wien 6
Raan thok eben kuat et ci yen yok thin aleng yic bi gam ka ye raan lengyic eloongiic.
Wien 7
Raan thok eben aathong nhiim eloong nhiim, kua len yic bi liek ekoeuny thong nhoem ka cin tiel bi loong kak tiit.
Wien 8
Raan thok eben alen yic bi luk ebanypanden nhiimbi yicde yok ci min eyith tueng e loong kek gam yen.
Wien 9
Ran thok eben aci leu bi doem kemen dampiny, kemen coeb ewei baai edieny.
Wien 10
Raan thok eben aleng yic bi nhoem agit ka koc kok, bi lungde ting elueok pathiic bi yek yicde ekoc nhiim ku kak ci gaemroet, ku kuat emeny ci yen meeny goeup.
Wien 11
Kuat eraan ci meeny, acin goeup awuc get te bi long yen nyooth lon le yen goeup awuc ekoc nhiim ku kony bi rot koeuny bei.
Raan aci luk ewei erin eken ci loei kemen ci kuec bi loei, ke ce yen awuc ye long ebaai nyooth, kemen long epinynhoem, te wen yen looi yen rot thin.
Wien 12
Acin raan ekeec epir eraande yic, kemen pande ku gonde kua thorkeiic kemen bi dhol ku rec erin edieny, ku raan eben aleng yic bi long koeuny ekak cit ekak yiic.
Wien 13
Raan eben aleng yic bi ceeth te wic ku loc te den ereer egan akeu thok eben ebaai yic.
Raan eben aleng yic bi la te wic epiny nhoem agut panden kua len yic bi dhok thin.
Wien 14
Raan eben aleng yic bi kook pandet, kemen bi them bi kook thin ka kat ekoeuc cieng.
Kuat eraan ci kang yath elukic awuc ca awuc ewel ebaai kemen bi lui eke ce roem kek eloong (UN), acii leng yic bi liek eyic ken yic.
Wien 15
Raan eben aleng yic bi rot yek anyoeoeth loen eyen ran ebaai.
Aci leu bi raan pen wer erot edieny, kemen bi jai loen ci yende yic bi rot war.
Wien 16
Moc ku tik te ci kek roun etheek doeoet, aaleng yic bik ker eboei ku loeike mith ka cinic ale kemen yath kua leng yiith thoeng nyiin ethiekic ku loui yic ku poek yic.
Thiek ci loi ka kic ekoc thiek rot gaem kua ci mec ekek.
Moc ku tik kek aamaatic tueng ebaai, kua leng yic bik liek ekoeuny baai ku baai nhoem.
Wien 17
Raan eben alen yic bi leng kede erot, kemen bi rom kek koc kok.
Aci leu bi raan peec cin bei ekake edieny.
Wien 18
Raan eben aleng yic bi tak ka lau nhoem popuonde, yanhde kua leng yic bi yanhde waric kemen ke ye theek kua leng yic bi pioc ku yeknhoem ku nyooyh ku tiit ka thien keme ekoc nhiim.
Wien 19
Raan eben aleng yic bi wetde luel ka lau nhoem kue yic ken egaem ewel ka launhoem ka cin raan la thin ku y'ong ewel ku tektek ku ceel kek edhol ci takic ka ci luui aken ewuad.
Wien 20
Raan eben aleng yic bi met akutic kua kuut la lik.
Aci leu bi kuat eraan mat akut ci wic yic eriel.
Wien 21
Raan eben aloeng yic bi lui miric panden bi kuany egai ekoc ekuany.
Raan eben aleng yic bi lui ci min ekuat eraan lui baai.
Ke wic koc ebaai yen eya rie e mir. ku ke wic koc kene ekueny kueny bi kam bi yaa weenic ekuany aliklik ka koc thoeng nhiim kemen bi loui te wen bi raan cuet ka lau nhoem.
Wien 22
Raan eben ka ye raan aakutt ekociic aaleng yic bi koeny ekoc bai ku koc epinynhoem ka cit te ye panden ye loui thin ku yith epirde ku cieng ku weet ci rot pal athekde yic la tueng ku thiek yicde.
Wien 23
Raan eben aleng yic bi lui ku kuany ka cit te wic e yen kua leng yic bi koeny bi lui.
Raan eben aleng yic bi lui a riob thong nhoem eloi yic ka ci yic tiel.
Raan eben aleng yic bi riob ariob ci gam bi rot muk apth ku juak ekak awen bi pirde cokpiny.
Raan eben aleng yic bi dit ku met akuic bi ka ke tiit koth.
Wien 24
Raan eben aleng yic bi long kemen bi cin lau ku nyoth enin ken eloi ku kol cin yen loi thin.
Wien 25

Kuat eraan aleng yic bi pir ka piol goup ku mit puou ka pande ecampathic, kua leth ku ten enin ku ka wen ekoc kouny baai kua leng yic bi pir cok nyinic ke cii yen lui, ku tuany, kemen ci bael ku leer kemen ci dhioeb ku la kak awen epir mietic, ka leu yen cin thin.
Meth ku man aleng yic bi kek koeny ku muk kek apath ku mith eben athoeng nhiim bi kek tiit baai mith dheth moc kek ku mith e lim.
Wien 26
Kuat eraan aleng yic bi pioc kua dhil epioc epath tueeng, ku pioc tueeng adhil emac eya nhoem, kua pioc eteet ku loi loi ecin ku col pioc den la tueeng apiolic, bi nhoem thoeng ka jang.
Ku weet ke ku bi thiekic ku thek ka ye raan ku lau enhoem la tueeng e cieng ku pelpiny ewel ku maeaeth ekem e wuuut ku la kuut, ku koeny thaai epinynhoem bi door muk.
Warken emith aleng yic bik mithken weet cit te wicke.
Wien 27
Kuat eraan aleng yic bi met ka lau nhoem epir ekoc ebaai yic, ku bi liek eteetic kua jueer erin ela tueeng epioc ku bi kak bi ben bei yhin kec koeuny.
Kuat eraan aleng yic bi ka path ku cieng ken epioc tiit.
Wien 28
Kuat eraan aleng yic bi liek ecieng ekoc epinynhoemic, bi yithke ku lau enhoem ci nyooth eceel ken yic yok egai.
Wien 29
Raan eben adhil koc loui bi yen nyouth lon te yen ekociic bi dit ka lau nhoem.

Raan eben adhil yithke thaap ka kacit te ci loong yen nyouth thin bigemgem e yith e koc koek, ku lau e nhoemde kua thekden, ku jol aathoeng nhoem e loiloi yiic, ku ka poth eyok eben ku jam aatheek ecieng ekoc epaan ekec thong nhiim.
Aci rot kang leu ather bi yith kak thaap ka ce te wen wic thai epiny nhoem ke thin.
Wien 30
Acin wet leu bi war kemen bi cokpiny e ceel ken yic ku luel ala ka ci pan ken kemen raan ken aci looi bi lyiith ku lauenhoem ci ben thin rac.
